reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good cabinet. Better price than big box store and just as good.
reviews.reviewText: Well packed. Easier to assemble with two people, but I managed on saw horses and used masking tape to hold some parts while I lined things up.All parts were in great condition. Fit and finish were good. I could not insert door lock rod bushings, but it works fine without them.Weighs about 95 lbs. Sturdy enough to store misc office supplies, but not likely to serve as a storage spot for cases of papers or heavy tool chests.Nice and deep; about 18" interior depth. The shelves are adjustable.I would buy again.

reviews.reviewText: When you handle the cabinet, you will instantly get a sense of how durable it is due to the fact that it is manufactured out of strong steel. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 23, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Way better than I though!
reviews.reviewText: Excellent in the way they package it. Coved on all sides and with metal corner guards to protect everything. Super easy to assemble as I did it myself. During assembly I kept think if it will be sturdy as the metal is very flimsy. As it kept getting assembled, it kept gaining strength. In the end, it is a very sturdy cabinet with so much space to store everything you have. I used it for my medical spa and it held everything with more room left over. I have placed 5 big boxes of 12 1000cc saline in each box in the bottom shelf. And it holds it with no effort. The doors are strong and solid. The handle and locking mechanism is very strong. Overall, I was very impressed with this cabinet.
